Subject: Jewish archives--Italy--Ancona.|~|Ancona (Italy)--History.
Description.note: Collection consists of Hebrew manuscripts, including Kabala (mysticism), prayer books, poetry, synagogue records from the Jewish community of Ancona, Italy, printed official documents relating to the Jews of Ancona, and about 50 Italian manuscripts.
